All Star PT Mira Mesa

Internship as a Student physical therapist
CI: Allen Maskell PT, DPT

In the summer of 2023, I was fortunate to work as a Student Physical Therapist at All Star Physical Therapy in Mira Mesa. All Star PT is an in-network outpatient orthopedic physical therapy clinic. Throughout my internship, I was able to learn how an in-network clinic is run and how to be both effective for my patients and a productive asset to the clinic. I was able to treat a variety of post-operative conditions, notably complex foot surgeries and shoulder surgeries. This is the first time I dealt with a patient experiencing post-op complication of hyperalgesia and through pain neuroscience education my CI and I were able to help this patient manage their pain and return to normal life.
